**Scapegoat** | Town Miscellaneous
__Basics__
The **scapegoat** believes themself to be a town civilian. The first time the **scapegoat** would die from a *basic attack*, they will survive. The attacker will learn the **scapegoat**'s role, and the next time the attacker would be lynched, the **scapegoat** is lynched in their place.
